      "title": "Executive Summary",
      "content": {
        "summary": "The financial report for 2026 shows payroll variances exceeding budget across multiple departments, with the highest variance in October (STR4764) at $4,935. Student payment collections missed targets in June due to overdue payments, and unresolved data quality issues require human review. These issues impact annual financial goals and require immediate attention to prevent further budget deviations.",
